{"type": "article", "id": 25646, "title": "挂在桌下的脚踏", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-19T07:12:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702170327bgF7alprR6cZSuj2.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个挂在桌下的脚踏板帮助久坐的人燃烧卡路里以及血液循环，它使用了类似书包肩带作为支撑结构，保持了一定的弹性并能收缩长短，让两只脚一直晃动。可以连接上 app 来监测消耗的热量。它还有另一款是完全独立的，让坐在沙发上的人也能活动起来。设计者芝加哥的工作室 MAYO Clinic，产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/hovr-unconsciously-burn-more-calories-at-work#/\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170324uSIvTJ6dVRtUrfle.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170325DYq75AXU6abFInso.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170325IQJHpo3CNcsaPzLe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170326dZG7nNehMqRDFKEb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9075\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021703261JD78Ya3RscMEbdi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}